            "id": 5928909,
            "title": "龍源電力(00916)發電量3月跌逾2%,首季跌逾4%",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　《經濟通通訊社9日專訊》龍源電力(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00916:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00916\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00916-HK</a>)(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:001289:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/001289\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">001289-CN</a>)公布,3月按合併報表口徑發電量約756.7萬兆瓦時,按年下降2.46%,主因去年10月起不再擁有火電控股裝機,3月未產生火電發電量。至於風電發電量同比增長7.57%,光伏發電量同比增長45.63%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　該集團指,今年首季累計發電量約2028.6萬兆瓦時,下降4.42%;剔除火電影響同比增長8.81%,其中風電增長4.37%,光伏增長55.65%。(wh)</p></section><section><p class=\"\"></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--></main>",
